{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1779174624326,"sessionID":"ses_1c0ee2f7cffeaYbr5us215mGuC","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"webfetch","callID":"call_02_exjQP1LZtMfP0WhjBZkb4642","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"url":"https://www.zillow.com/rental-manager/","format":"markdown","timeout":30},"output":"Zillow Rental Manager - Online Property Management Tools             \n\n[Zillow Home](/)\n\n[Sign In](https://www.zillow.com/rental-manager/login/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.zillow.com%2Frental-manager%2F)\n\n[![Zillow Rentals Logo](https://nodes3cdn.hotpads.com/zrm-marketing-web/15438/_next/static/media/rentals-logo-vr.1ee11c44.svg)](/rental-manager/)\n\n[Contact sales](/rentals-network/contact-sales/)[Post your listing](/rental-manager/properties?postingPath=true)\n\n-   [Rental manager](/rental-manager/)Open Rental manager menu\n    \n    -   [Price my rental](/rental-manager/price-my-rental/)\n    -   [Listing](/rental-manager/post-a-listing/)\n    -   [Applications](/rental-manager/tenant-screening/)\n    -   [Leases](/rental-manager/rental-lease-agreements/)\n    -   [Payment](/rental-manager/collect-rent-online/)\n    \n-   [Apartment advertising](/rentals-network/rental-advertising/)Open Apartment advertising menu\n    \n    -   [Subscription based ads](/rentals-network/rent-connect/)\n    -   [Pay-per-lease ads](/rentals-network/lease-connect/)\n    -   [Syndicate listings](/rentals-network/listing-feeds/)\n    \n-   [Resources](/rentals-network/resources/)\n\n[Contact sales](/rentals-network/contact-sales/)[Post your listing](/rental-manager/properties?postingPath=true)\n\n[Post your listing](/rental-manager/properties?postingPath=true)[Contact sales](/rentals-network/contact-sales/)\n\n![Photo of woman working at a desk with computer and houseplant, representing confident property management.](https://delivery.digitallibrary.zillowgroup.com/public/SZ_Rentals_Rental-Manager_Hero_1920x712_Desktop_png_Original.png)\n\n# Level up your landlording simply and confidently\n\nTake the extra legwork out of running your rental. From leases and payments to maintenance and move-out, Rental Manager has the tools to help you get more done.\n\n[Get started](https://www.zillow.com/rental-manager/properties/)\n\n[Get started](https://www.zillow.com/rental-manager/properties/)[View paid services](http://www.zillow.com/rental-manager/tenant-placement?from=zrm_homepage)\n\nAlready have an account? **[Sign in](https://www.zillow.com/rental-manager/login/?url=%2Frental-manager%2Fproperties%3FpostingPath%3Dtrue)**\n\n![](https://delivery.digitallibrary.zillowgroup.com/public/SZ_Rentals_Rental-Manager_Hero_343x296_Mobile_png_CMS_Extra_Large.auto)\n\n## Rent like a pro with Rental Manager\n\nPosting a listing is just the beginning. Build and sign leases, screen tenants, collect rent and fill vacancies with over 30 million monthly visitors.\n\n[Get started for free](https://www.zillow.com/rental-manager/properties?postingPath=true)\n\n![Icon: document with checkmark representing posting listings.](https://delivery.digitallibrary.zillowgroup.com/public/SZ_Icon_HouseClock_44x44_png_CMS_Extra_Large.auto)\n\n## Post listings & find renters quickly and easily\n\nCreate listings in minutes to reach the most visitors of any rentals network\\*.\n\n[Learn more](https://www.zillow.com/rental-manager/collect-rent-online/)\n\n![Icon: document with pencil representing creating and sending leases.](https://www.zillowstatic.com/bedrock/app/uploads/sites/51/2025/12/Duocolor-icon.png)\n\n## Create & send leases for signing\n\nBuild a new lease online or upload your own for signing. Our lease tools make it simple.\n\n[Learn more](https://www.zillow.com/rental-manager/)\n\n![Icon: credit card representing online rent collection.](https://delivery.digitallibrary.zillowgroup.com/public/SZ_Icon_PiggyBank_44x44_png_CMS_Extra_Large.auto)\n\n## Collect rent online\n\nGet paid for rent, utilities, move-in fees and more for free.\n\n[Learn more](https://www.zillow.com/rental-manager/collect-rent-online/)\n\n![Icon: new managing tours](https://delivery.digitallibrary.zillowgroup.com/public/SZ_Rentals_Rental-Manager_New_Pill_png_CMS_Extra_Large.auto)\n\n## Manage tours effortlessly\n\nSave time coordinating tours by letting renters know upfront when you’re free.\n\n[![Photo of living room with pricing widget overlay showing rent estimate and availability.](https://delivery.digitallibrary.zillowgroup.com/public/SZ_Rentals_Rental-Manager_Price_671x400_Desktop_png_CMS_Extra_Large.auto)](https://delivery.digitallibrary.zillowgroup.com/public/SZ_Rentals_Rental-Manager_Price_671x400_Desktop_png_Original.png)\n\n## Take the guesswork out of managing your business\n\n**Price your rental competitively.** Use our pricing tools to optimize the return on investment for your property.\n\n[Get started](https://www.zillow.com/rental-manager/price-my-rental/)\n\n## Here’s what the pros are saying\n\nPrevious itemsNext items\n\n-   ![Left quote card: quotation mark icon in blue.](https://www.zillowstatic.com/bedrock/app/uploads/sites/51/2025/12/Quote-light.svg)\n    \n    Zillow simplifies the whole rental process from listing to leasing to applications and payments.\n    \n    ****Jeff C.****  \n    OK\n    \n-   ![Left quote card: quotation mark icon in blue.](https://www.zillowstatic.com/bedrock/app/uploads/sites/51/2025/12/Quote-dark.svg)\n    \n    With Zillow Rental Manager it was easy to accept messages from potential tenants, easy to accept and screen applications (including credit/background checks), and even create a lease!  Everything was nicely integrated into one interface, making it simple and centralized.\n    \n    **Greg C.**  \n    TX\n    \n-   ![quote icon](https://www.zillowstatic.com/bedrock/app/uploads/sites/51/2025/12/Quote-light.svg)\n    \n    I personally have 20 rentals and I have every unit on Zillow Rental Manager. It’s not the only platform I choose to use but I do like it and generate all my leases using it.\n    \n    **Joe W.**  \n    FL\n    \n-   ![quote icon](https://www.zillowstatic.com/bedrock/app/uploads/sites/51/2025/12/Quote-dark.svg)\n    \n    While Zillow kept the steps to rent my property simple, the process and outcome were excellent. I’ve found a renter and the process of building and signing the lease through Zillow were great! Thank-you!\n    \n    **Veronica P.**  \n    WI\n    \n\n## Here’s what the pros are saying\n\nPrevious itemsNext items\n\n-   ![quote icon](https://www.zillowstatic.com/bedrock/app/uploads/sites/51/2025/12/Quote-light.svg)\n    \n    Zillow simplifies the whole rental process from listing to leasing to applications and payments.\n    \n    ****Jeff C.****  \n    OK\n    \n-   ![quote icon](https://www.zillowstatic.com/bedrock/app/uploads/sites/51/2025/12/Quote-dark.svg)\n    \n    With Zillow Rental Manager it was easy to accept messages from potential tenants, easy to accept and screen applications (including credit/background checks), and even create a lease!  Everything was nicely integrated into one interface, making it simple and centralized.\n    \n    **Greg C.**  \n    TX\n    \n-   ![quote icon](https://www.zillowstatic.com/bedrock/app/uploads/sites/51/2025/12/Quote-light.svg)\n    \n    I personally have 20 rentals and I have every unit on Zillow Rental Manager. It’s not the only platform I choose to use but I do like it and generate all my leases using it.\n    \n    **Joe W.**  \n    FL\n    \n-   ![quote icon](https://www.zillowstatic.com/bedrock/app/uploads/sites/51/2025/12/Quote-dark.svg)\n    \n    While Zillow kept the steps to rent my property simple, the process and outcome were excellent. I’ve found a renter and the process of building and signing the lease through Zillow were great! Thank-you!\n    \n    **Veronica P.**  \n    WI\n    \n\n## Here’s what the pros are saying\n\nPrevious itemsNext items\n\n-   ![quote icon](https://www.zillowstatic.com/bedrock/app/uploads/sites/51/2025/12/Quote-light.svg)\n    \n    Zillow 