{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1779174842592,"sessionID":"ses_1c0ee2f7cffeaYbr5us215mGuC","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"call_00_3k2P7Rrkh1F9t3WqRisS0262","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/design/DOMAIN_RESEARCH.md","content":"# Domain Research\n\n## Industry\n\n**Industry:** Real Estate Rental Listings / Property Rental Platforms\n\n**Domain:** `nestfind.com` — Web application\n\n**Market Context:**\nThe online rental property market is dominated by several large aggregator platforms in the US (Zillow, Redfin, Apartments.com, Realtor.com). These platforms serve as two-sided marketplaces connecting renters searching for properties with landlords and property managers listing available units. The rental segment represents a distinct vertical from home buying, with its own user behaviors: shorter decision cycles, price-driven filtering, and frequent comparison shopping.\n\n**Key Differentiators in the Market:**\n- All major competitors aggregate MLS + direct listing data\n- Some are broader real estate portals (Zillow, Redfin) that cover buying, selling, renting, mortgages\n- Others are rental-specialized (Rent.com, ApartmentGuide, HotPads)\n- Admin/landlord tools are often a separate product offering (Zillow Rental Manager)\n- Map-based search is universal\n\n## Competitors\n\n### 1. Zillow Rentals\n- **URL:** zillow.com/homes/for_rent/\n- **Company:** Zillow Group (public)\n- **Scale:** 30+ million monthly visitors across the rentals network\n- **Coverage:** Nationwide US, rentals + sales + mortgages\n- **Key UI Patterns:**\n  - **Landing Page:** Hero section with prominent search bar (location input). Navigation tabs split into Buy / Rent / Sell / Mortgage / Agent. Search results split-view: map on right, property cards on left.\n  - **Property Cards:** Photo thumbnail, price (prominent, bold), beds/baths count, address, square footage. Heart icon for favorites. Badges for price drops, new listings, 3D tours.\n  - **Detail Page:** Full-width photo carousel, sticky sidebar with price + key stats + contact form, detailed description, amenities grid, Google Maps embed, school/neighborhood info.\n  - **Favorites:** Saved via heart icon, accessible from top nav \"Favorites\" link. Requires login.\n  - **Filters:** Price range, beds/baths, property type (apartment, house, condo, townhouse), home type, square footage, pets, amenities.\n  - **Admin Side (Rental Manager):** Separate subdomain. Features: Post listings, tenant screening, lease management, rent collection, tour scheduling, pricing tools.\n- **Sub-brands:** HotPads (map-centric rental search), Trulia, StreetEasy.\n\n### 2. Redfin Rentals\n- **URL:** redfin.com/rentals\n- **Company:** Redfin Corporation (Rocket Companies subsidiary)\n- **Scale:** Nationwide, integrated with full Redfin platform\n- **Coverage:** Nationwide US, buying + renting\n- **Key UI Patterns:**\n  - **Landing Page:** Search-forward. \"Your perfect rental one search away\" hero. Clear separation between For Sale and Rent.\n  - **Renter Dashboard:** Dedicated renter area with saved searches, favorites, rental tools.\n  - **Rental Resources:** Market tracker, rent-vs-buy calculator, affordability calculator, first-time renter guide.\n  - **Property Cards:** Similar to Zillow — photos, price, beds/baths, address, square footage.\n  - **App Strategy:** Heavy push for mobile app with QR code download.\n  - **List Your Home for Rent:** Direct path for landlords to list properties.\n- **Subsidiary Brands:** Rent.com (rental-specialized), ApartmentGuide (apartment-focused).\n\n### 3. Rent.com\n- **URL:** rent.com\n- **Company:** Rent Group Inc. (Redfin subsidiary)\n- **Scale:** Rental-focused platform\n- **Coverage:** Nationwide US, rental-exclusive\n- **Key UI Patterns:**\n  - **Landing Page:** \"Find your perfect place\" — image-based hero with search bar. Clean, minimal design.\n  - **Trending Properties:** Grid of property cards below hero with prices, price-drop badges, move-in specials (e.g., \"1 Month Free\").\n  - **Favorites:** \"Saved\" count in header, similar heart/favorite pattern.\n  - **Mobile-first:** Strong app download promotion with QR code.\n  - **Renter Blog/Resources:** Integrated blog for tips and guides.\n  - **Near Me Searches:** Prominent \"Apartments Near Me\", \"Houses Near Me\" shortcuts by bedroom count and budget tier.\n- **Sister Brand:** ApartmentGuide.com — nearly identical UI pattern, apartment-exclusive focus.\n\n### 4. HotPads\n- **URL:** hotpads.com\n- **Company:** Zillow Group\n- **Scale:** Niche/map-centric\n- **Coverage:** Nationwide US\n- **Key UI Patterns:**\n  - **Map-first:** The map dominates the UI; property cards overlay as a scrollable list. This is the primary differentiator from Zillow's split-view.\n  - **Quick Filters:** Location-centric filters on map view.\n\n### 5. Apartments.com\n- **URL:** apartments.com\n- **Company:** CoStar Group\n- **Scale:** Large commercial player\n- **Coverage:** Nationwide US, apartment-focused\n- **Key UI Patterns:**\n  - **Landing Page:** Search bar with location. Apartment-focused branding.\n  - **Listings:** Grid of property cards with community photos, starting price range, unit counts.\n  - **Property Detail:** Community overview, floor plans, amenities, resident reviews.\n\n## Reference UI Patterns\n\n### Universal Patterns Across All Competitors\n\n1. **Prominent Search Bar on Landing**\n   - Every competitor places a large, central search input on the homepage. The default/primary input is location (city, ZIP, neighborhood). Zillow uses natural-language parsing (\"3 bedroom townhouse with fireplace in Seattle, WA\").\n\n2. **Property Card Design**\n   ```text\n   +---------------------------+\n   |      [Photo / Carousel]   |\n   |                           |\n   +---------------------------+\n   | $1,995/mo   [heart icon]  |\n   | 2 bd · 2 ba · 1,200 sqft |\n   | 123 Main St, Austin, TX   |\n   | [Badge: New | Price Drop]  |\n   +---------------------------+\n   ```\n   - Photo is the dominant visual element (2:1 or 3:2 aspect ratio)\n   - Price is the most prominent text element (largest font, bold)\n   - Beds, baths, square footage on one compact line\n   - Address below\n   - Heart/favorite icon in top-right of card or inline\n   - Optional badges: \"New\", \"Price Drop\", \"1 Month Free\", \"Popular\"\n\n3. **Search Results: Map + List Split View**\n   - Universal pattern: map occupies 50-60% of the screen (right side on desktop), card list scrolls on the other side\n   - Filters bar above results: Price (min-max), Beds, Baths, Property Type, More Filters\n   - \"Save Search\" button for email alerts\n   - Sort dropdown: \"Newest\", \"Price (Low to High)\", \"Price (High to Low)\"\n\n4. **Filters Panel**\n   - Price range (double-ended slider or min/max inputs)\n   - Bedrooms (buttons: Studio, 1, 2, 3, 4+)\n   - Bathrooms (buttons: 1, 1.5, 2, 3+)\n   - Property type (checkboxes: Apartment, House, Condo, Townhouse)\n   - Amenities (checkboxes: In-unit laundry, Parking, Pool, Gym, Pet-friendly, A/C)\n   - Square footage range\n   - Move-in date / availability\n\n5. **Favorites System**\n   - Heart icon on every property card (filled when favorited)\n   - Dedicated \"Favorites\" page/route\n   - Requires authentication to persist\n   - \"Saved\" count indicator in navigation\n\n6. **Inquiry / Contact Flow**\n   - Contact form on property detail page\n   - Fields: Name, Email, Phone, Message\n   - \"Request a Tour\" or \"Contact Property\" CTAs\n   - Confirmation after submission\n\n7. **Admin / Property Management Dashboard**\n   - Separate section or subdomain\n   - Key sections: Properties (list/manage), Inquiries (inbox), Applications, Leases, Payments\n   - Statistics overview (total listings, leads, recent activity)\n   - Table-based list views with actions (edit, delete, archive)\n\n### Navigation Patterns\n\n| Element | Convention |\n|---------|-----------|\n| Logo | Top-left, links to home |\n| Main Nav Tabs | Buy / Rent / Sell / Mortgage / Manage (for Zillow), or Home / Search / Favorites / Dashboard (for simpler apps) |\n| Sign In / Join | Top-right |\n| Favorites | Top nav, heart icon or \"Favorites\" text |\n| Footer | City/state browse links, company links, app download |\n\n## Page-type Conventions\n\n### Landing/Home Page\n\nStandard sections observed across competitors:\n\n| Section | Purpose | Prevalence |\n|---------|---------|-----------|\n| Hero + Search Bar | Primary CTA: location search with optional text input | 100% |\n| Value Proposition | 1-2 line headline (e.g., \"Find your perfect place\", \"Your perfect rental one search away\") | 100% |\n| Trending/Featured Properties | Grid of property cards to demonstrate inventory | 80% |\n| Popular Searches | Quick links: \"Apartments Near Me\", \"Apartments by City\", \"Houses by City\" | 100% |\n| App Download CTA | QR code + app store badges | 80% |\n| Rental Resources / Blog | Tips, affordabilty calculators, market trends | 60% |\n| \"List Your Property\" CTA | Path for landlords to post listings | 60% |\n| Footer | City/state browse links, company links, Equal Housing logo | 100% |\n\n**NestFind Landing Page Recommended Sections:**\n1. Hero with search bar (location + optional filters)\n2. Featured rental properties grid (3-6 cards)\n3. Popular cities/regions quick links\n4. How it works (3-step: Search → Compare → Inquire)\n5. For property managers: \"List your property\" CTA\n6. Footer with city links\n\n### Search/Listing Page\n\nStandard layout:\n\n```\n+---------------------------------------------------+\n| [Search Bar: Location] [Price] [Beds] [Type] [Filters] [Save Search] |\n+---------------------------------------------------+\n|                  |                                  |\n|  Property Card   |                                  |\n|  Property Card   |          MAP VIEW                |\n|  Property Card   |                                  |\n|  Property Card   |                                  |\n|  Property Card   |                                  |\n|  [Pagination]    |                                  |\n+---------------------------------------------------+\n```\n\n**NestFind Search Page Recommended Sections:**\n1. Sticky search/filter bar\n2. Filter sidebar or horizontal filter chips: Price, Beds, Baths, Property Type, Amenities\n3. Sort dropdown (Newest, Price Low→High, Price High→Low)\n4. Property card list (scrollable)\n5. Map view (Google Maps embed with markers)\n6. \"Save Search\" action\n7. Results count (\"42 properties found\")\n8. Pagination or infinite scroll\n\n### Property Detail Page\n\nStandard layout from top to bottom:\n\n```\n+---------------------------------------------------+\n| Photo Carousel / Gallery (full-width, ~400px high)  |\n+---------------------------------------------------+\n| [Back to Search]                                   |\n| Title: \"Modern 2BR Apartment in Downtown Austin\"   |\n| Address · Price · Beds/Baths · Sqft · Available    |\n| [Save/Favorite] [Share]                            |\n+---------------------------------------------------+\n|              |  [Inquiry Form]                      |\n| Description  |  Name: ______                        |\n|              |  Email: ______                       |\n| Amenities    |  Phone: ______                       |\n| Floor Plan   |  Message: ______                     |\n| Location Map |  [Send Message]                      |\n| Similar Listings                                     |\n+---------------------------------------------------+\n```\n\n**NestFind Property Detail Recommended Sections:**\n1. Photo gallery/carousel (multiple images)\n2. Property title + quick stats (price, beds, baths, sqft, property type)\n3. Key CTA buttons: \"Save to Favorites\" (heart toggle), \"Submit Inquiry\"\n4. Overview / Description (rich text)\n5. Amenities grid/list with icons\n6. Floor plan image (if available)\n7. Property details table (year built, parking, pet policy, laundry, etc.)\n8. Google Maps embed (location)\n9. Inquiry / Contact form (Name, Email, Phone, Message)\n10. Similar/recommended properties\n\n### Dashboard (Admin)\n\nZillow Rental Manager model:\n\n```\n+---------------------------------------------------+\n| Sidebar            |  Dashboard Content             |\n| - Properties       |                                |\n| - Inquiries        |  [Stats Cards]                 |\n| - Applications     |  Total Properties | Inquiries   |\n| - Leases           |  Recent Activity               |\n| - Payments         |                                |\n| - Pricing Tools    |  [Recent Inquiries Table]      |\n|                    |  [Recent Listings Table]       |\n+---------------------------------------------------+\n```\n\n**NestFind Admin Dashboard Recommended Sections:**\n1. Sidebar navigation: Properties, Inquiries, Users\n2. Overview statistics cards: Total Properties, Total Inquiries, Total Users, Recent Activity\n3. Properties table: Title, Price, Status, Actions (Edit, Delete)\n4. Inquiries table: Property, Renter Name, Date, Status (New/Read/Responded), Actions\n5. Add/Edit Property form: Multi-field form with photo upload\n6. Inquiry detail view: Renter info, message, property link, respond action\n7. User management table (view-only for NestFind scope)\n\n### Favorites Page\n- Grid of saved property cards (same card pattern as search results)\n- \"Remove from Favorites\" action on each card\n- Empty state: \"No saved properties yet. Start browsing!\"\n- Accessible from main navigation (heart icon)\n\n### Authentication Pages\n- Login page: Email + Password form, \"Forgot Password?\" link, \"Create Account\" link\n- Registration page: Name, Email, Password, Phone (optional)\n- Forgot Password page: Email input, \"Send Reset Link\" button\n- Clean, centered card layout (not full-width hero)\n\n## Competitor Feature Matrix\n\n| Feature | Zillow | Redfin | Rent.com | ApartmentGuide | NestFind Target |\n|---------|--------|--------|----------|----------------|-----------------|\n| Property Search | Yes | Yes | Yes | Yes | Yes |\n| Location/Map View | Yes | Yes | Limited | Limited | Yes (Google Maps) |\n| Price Filter | Yes | Yes | Yes | Yes | Yes |\n| Bed/Bath Filters | Yes | Yes | Yes | Yes | Yes |\n| Property Type Filter | Yes | Yes | Yes | Yes (apt only) | Yes |\n| Photo Gallery | Yes | Yes | Yes | Yes | Yes |\n| Favorites | Yes | Yes | Yes | Yes | Yes |\n| Inquiry/Contact | Yes | Yes | Yes | Yes | Yes |\n| Admin Dashboard | Yes (Rental Manager) | Yes | Yes (List Property) | Yes (List Community) | Yes |\n| Apps/Screening | Yes | No | No | No | No (MVP) |\n| Leases | Yes | No | No | No | No (MVP) |\n| Rent Collection | Yes | No | No | No | No (MVP) |\n| Mortgage/Buy | Yes | Yes | No | No | No (out of scope) |\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/design/DOMAIN_RESEARCH.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":".claude-project/nestfind/design/DOMAIN_RESEARCH.md","time":{"start":1779174842318,"end":1779174842591}},"id":"prt_e3f13a8f10013orENPm66OZz4i","sessionID":"ses_1c0ee2f7cffeaYbr5us215mGuC","messageID":"msg_e3f139b4d001KUW94qHsmgaUAX"}}
